save_citation_one
   _Saveframe_category           citation

   _Citation_full               
;
Ye, X. M., Pochapsky, T. C. and Pochapsky, S. S., 
"1H NMR Sequential Assignments and Identification of Secondary 
Structural Elements in Oxidized Putidaredoxin, an Electron-transfer 
Protein from Pseudomonas,"  Biochemistry 31, 1961-1968 (1992)
;
